{
  "stem": "7069.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my brother when we were separated, my brother assumed-- and absolutely correctly-- that in the condition that I was, I had no chance to make it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me maybe a day or two, then I would be trampled to death in the squeezing and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Absolutely correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would have looked at it the identical way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was just condemned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he didn't even look for me for that reason.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was 100% sure-- not knowing what happened to me in the meantime, of course-- that I hadn't made it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Until some mutual acquaintance-- he stayed in Munich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't even want to go back to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until some mutual acquaintance pointed out to me that he had seen me, which he had a heck of a time to convince them that it was me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, we couldn't see each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in Berlin and he-- and he was in Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was no telephone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing that you could do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No telephone, even letter writing didn't work very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This-- this-- this person that we talked to told me that my brother, being a cantor, was immediately doing his duty as a cantor, because there were no other cantors alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And would sing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he would also do Friday night services over the radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, not regularly over the radio, but I was doing one Friday night-- part of a Friday night service over the radio.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somehow, he was able to turn the radio on in Munich and to hear me, and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, and I heard him from Munich doing his thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
